Class Customer

  • java.lang.Object
    • Person
      • Customer
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Retail_Customer
    public class Customer
extends Person
    The Customer class represents a customer entity, extending from the Person class. It contains information about the customer such as their orders and operator ID.
